\DOC by

\TYPE {by : tactic -> refinement}

\SYNOPSIS
Converts a tactic to a refinement.

\DESCRIBE
The call {by tac} for a tactic {tac} gives a refinement of the current list of
subgoals that applies {tac} to the first subgoal.

\COMMENTS
Only of interest to users who want to handle `refinements' explicitly.

\ENDDOC
